  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Block Alteste, the guy who was in charge on the barracks, if it wasn't enough what they did with us, would put that barrel down.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You'd have to line up there to get a cup and your daily ration of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if one guy or another didn't like the way we were moving, or the way we were standing, or the way we were receiving our-- our food, he took the whole barrel, emptied it on the floor, and that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and most of us, because we were really starving for a little moisture-- we were completely dehydrated-- used to lie down on the ground to, like, sip the-- the-- the moisture off the ground, from the mud, just to get a little fluid in your body.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the human-- the dehumanizing of-- of the population there was to such an extent that-- that the worst they can perform, the more-- the Germans didn't even have to do the job.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the Germans did during the day-- they used to come in and just count us, in the morning, as we marched out from the camps, and in the evening, as we came back to the camps.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all they were interested in is the body count was correct.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the daily sight was that, if somebody died at work-- which was very common-- or somebody died on the road because he was beaten up by anybody who could just raise his hand and wanted to do so-- all they were interested, that all the dead bodies were accounted for.",
      "word_count": 55
    }
  ],
